---
title: Cheat's Beef & Corn Enchiladas with Cheddar Cheese & Yoghurt
description: Everyone loves enchiladas, but we've made them even more lovable by getting them on the table quicker. This version uses the grill to melt the cheese, and adds corn and carrot to the beef mixture for extra flavour and texture.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheats-beef-corn-enchiladas-e567524b.jpg
